<div class="title">Fantastically Visual</div>
<div class="substance">AMT</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Backspace&Exact=1">Backspace</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Backspace. "Fantastically Visual: An Experience with AMT (exp21750)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jan 22, 2008. erowid.org/exp/21750</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

